1. The program chooses a word randomly from a file.
2. The player must enter a 5 letter word.
3. If a letter is exists but is not at the right place, display it yellow, if the letter is placed. correctly, display it green and if it is not in the word, display it gray.
4. The program ask the name of the player.
5. Make a number of wins file with the top 10 players.
6. At each end game, display the score board.


Notes :
	- all words have the same size (5 characters)
	- after 5 guesses, the player has lost
